# Matthew Edeker

## Operator Technology Infrastructure Group

Phone: **512-475-9411** |
Email: **[medeker@tacc.utexas.edu](mailto:medeker@tacc.utexas.edu)**

Matt joined TACC in August 2016. In his role as an operator, Matt monitors the systems that TACC has onsite in the data center. He also takes care of individual IT needs such as setting up laptops for new employees and addressing tickets during the afterhours of business operations. Prior to TACC, Matt worked on the helpdesk for a company that developed software for drug studies in North Liberty, Iowa.

### Education

**B.A., English,**  

University of Iowa